born as they learn how to walk.\nBut you'll be able to save all the slippers.\n\nA new concept of shooting puzzle game.\nIt is a shooting puzzle game that makes a way for AI characters wandering in a maze to move easily and safely.\n\n100 stages with various solutions.\nVarious maze shapes, slippers, objects, and daemons are combined, so each stage can be played differently each time.", "short_description": "Save the slippers that are hanging in the maze of nightmares!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "(\ub370\ubaa8)(\ud55c\uae00)3000_900.png", "id": "429007318575366", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003276_429007321908699_4258283118475983943_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WJ7D-AomSmgQ7kNvgGvFsdi&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCROkGQX1hsRWTr0db_Is1wukApcQryS6SATI9qkB9eHQ&oe=670912AA"}, {"file_name": "\ub354\ud074\ub77c\uc774\uc5b8\ud2b8\ub85c\uace0(\ud55c\uae00).png", "id": "3213236945564295", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974517_3213236948897628_4786406447797518072_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VUaAhs-22HkQ7kNvgFfzbHN&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCmfYFJUOwZqp6g0YMm5HYhlFno6rDba0RJ5LmFYhjiJA&oe=6709255E"}, {"file_name": "(\ub370\ubaa8)(\ud55c\uae00)2560_1440.png", "id": "1042171706627527", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75429288_1042171713294193_695814847444454466_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xJS_Vq1Eit0Q7kNvgGa-951&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDjqitnqNjakcn7zMPc6zdlmclTJ_SJGbA7Wj9eE7Cvsg&oe=67091431"}, {"file_name": "(\ub370\ubaa8)(\ud55c\uae00)1080_360.png", "id": "938165583721864", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75195905_938165587055197_7689133019531011071_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_s